<a href="/articles/25555.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/25555/indexMediumPc2/25555.jpg?1460741386" alt="一篇偷窥狂报道，马上就要变成斯皮尔伯格和门德斯的电影">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">一篇偷窥狂报道，马上就要变成斯皮尔伯格和门德斯的电影</h1>
	</div>
